cff-version: 1.2.0
title: "protoBanana: OSS chat-native image generation + editing"
type: software
authors:
  - name: "protoLabsAI"
    email: "josh@protolabs.studio"
repository-code: "https://github.com/protoLabsAI/protoBanana"
url: "https://github.com/protoLabsAI/protoBanana"
abstract: >
  An open-source counterpart to Google's Nano-Banana / OpenAI's GPT-Image-2:
  a LiteLLM CustomLLM provider that fronts ComfyUI workflows for unified
  image generation, instruction edit, multi-reference compose, background
  removal, region-aware edit, inpaint, and outpaint. Routed via OpenAI
  /v1/chat/completions, /v1/images/generations, and /v1/images/edits.
  Backed by Qwen-Image-2512 + Qwen-Image-Edit-2511 + Florence-2 + SAM 2.1
  + BiRefNet/RMBG.
license: Apache-2.0
keywords:
  - image generation
  - image editing
  - litellm
  - comfyui
  - qwen-image
  - openai-compatible
